### Core URLs overview
- Dashboard (staff-only): `/` and `/dashboard/` → `dashboard_view` in [`core/views.py`](mdc:core/views.py)
- Health: `/health/` (Docker healthcheck) in [`core/urls.py`](mdc:core/urls.py)
- Manual triggers (staff-only):
  - `/trigger_scrape/` → `trigger_scrape_ajax`
  - `/trigger_analysis/` → `trigger_analysis_ajax`
- Trade management (staff-only):
  - Page: `/close-trade/` → `manual_close_trade_view`
  - APIs: `/api/close-trade/`, `/api/cancel-trade/`, `/api/trade-status/<id>/`
- System status and activity (staff-only):
  - `/system_status/`, `/api/system-status/` → `system_status_api`
  - `/api/recent-activities/` → `recent_activities_api`
- Scraping (staff-only): `/api/trigger-scrape/` → `trigger_scrape_api`
- Post analysis (staff-only): `/api/post-analysis/<post_id>/` → `get_post_analysis_ajax`
- Public posts (currently staff-protected): `/api/public-posts/` → `public_posts_api`

### DRF Router
- Mounted at `/api/` via [`core/urls.py`](mdc:core/urls.py), viewsets in [`core/api.py`](mdc:core/api.py):
